<subSubSection pageId="44" pageNumber="45" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="44.[151,1436,498,564]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,279,498,524]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
A species of the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Krefft, 1971 Pseudoscopelus scutatus Krefft" authorityYear="1971" box="[482,772,498,523]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="scutatus">
<emphasis box="[482,772,498,523]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Pseudoscopelus scutatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group, which can be distinguished from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Melo, Walker Jr. and Klepadlo, 2007 Pseudoscopelus bothrorrhinos Melo, Walker Jr. and Klepadlo" authorityYear="2007" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chiasmodontidae" genus="Pseudoscopelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bothrorrhinos">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">P. bothrorrhinos</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by a single characteristic: 
<emphasis box="[575,606,538,563]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">lpf</emphasis>
absent (
<emphasis box="[705,775,538,563]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">vs. lpf</emphasis>
present).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
