<geoCoordinate box="[1239,1320,1752,1778]" degrees="83" direction="west" orientation="longitude" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" precision="55555" value="-83.0">83° W</geoCoordinate>
. A single record in the Indian Ocean, from the Arabian Sea; from 
<geoCoordinate box="[804,900,1792,1818]" degrees="2" direction="north" minutes="00" orientation="latitude" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" precision="925" value="2.0">2°00’ N</geoCoordinate>
